2
00:00:41,904 --> 00:00:44,499
<i>His arrow's struck Lynn Weaver...</i>

3
00:00:44,708 --> 00:00:47,644
<i>...a talk-show host
worth $ 100 million...</i>

4
00:00:47,845 --> 00:00:51,611
<i>...whose popular program
has spawned a TV empire...</i>

5
00:00:51,816 --> 00:00:54,718
<i>...announced her marriage
this afternoon.</i>

6
00:00:54,919 --> 00:00:56,511
<i>The lucky groom-to-be...</i>

7
00:00:56,721 --> 00:01:00,557
<i>...is former NFL quarterback
and aging playboy Mike Gambril...</i>

8
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:04,456
<i>...who is a sportscaster
for NBC in Los Angeles.</i>

9
00:01:05,665 --> 00:01:08,259
You look good
with your collar up like that.

10
00:01:08,468 --> 00:01:10,493
<i>Mike, nice catch!</i>

11
00:01:25,487 --> 00:01:27,012
<i>Lynn Weaver and Mike Gambril...</i>

12
